{"tid":998381,"cid":20,"subCid":0,"title":"[電車撚] 政府放寬「一換一」計劃，持車期減至18個月","createTime":"2019-01-28T02:31:49.000Z","updateTime":"2019-01-29T07:34:32.000Z","uid":18074,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"6edadee983351b9db3dc7c798f2e5ad4b5b60d33","tid":998381,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:31:49.000Z","msg":"政府去年初推岀舊私家車更換電動車「一換一」的計劃，最多可獲25萬元稅項寬減，但計劃被批評關卡多，要求舊私家車車主連續持有該車3年才換車的條件「離地」、打擊車主換車意欲。政府今日(28日)宣佈，即日起放寬電動私家車「一換一」計劃下「擁有車輛期間」之參加條件，舊私家車車主只需連續持有該車18個月或以上，便可參加計劃。<br />\n<br />\n政府亦同時放寬領牌期間的條件，由「緊接在『舊私家車』取消登記前的24個月期間內須有最少20個月（即608天或以上），連續或不連續皆可，領有有效車輛牌照」，修訂為「緊接在『舊私家車』取消登記前的12個月期間內須有最少10個月（即304天或以上），連續或不連續皆可，領有有效車輛牌照」。"},{"pid":"da11e094bb5ac79178bd7e33f9979ada30ec16b1","tid":998381,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:33:05.000Z","msg":"睇黎遲啲成街都係model 3..."},{"pid":"07969e58bf4c99140537071ba53dc94394fecd58","tid":998381,"uid":33653,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"da11e094bb5ac79178bd7e33f9979ada30ec16b1","tid":998381,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:33:05.000Z","msg":"睇黎遲啲成街都係model 3..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:39:12.000Z","msg":"原本諗住班友換BYD, 點知Model 3 仲平"},{"pid":"7080385cedad5075f877f0c32206866bde3c01fc","tid":998381,"uid":9230,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"da11e094bb5ac79178bd7e33f9979ada30ec16b1","tid":998381,"uid":18074,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T02:33:05.000Z","msg":"睇黎遲啲成街都係model 3..."},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-01-28T03:00:26.000Z","msg":"維修連有錢佬都牙痛咁聲，班窮西<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" 